---
import PageLayout from '../../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

export const prerender = true;

const lang = 'en';
const title = 'History';
const pageTitle = 'History of the Organization';
---

<PageLayout title={title} lang={lang} pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <h2>Foundation</h2>
  <p>The Public Association «Counterpart-Sheriktesh» was founded in January 2002. The organization was established by a group of activists and human rights defenders united by the idea of strengthening civil society in Kyrgyzstan.</p>

  <h2>2002-2006: Early Years</h2>
  <p>In the early years, the organization focused on human rights monitoring and legal education of the population. The first projects on teaching citizens their rights and ways to protect them were implemented.</p>

  <h2>2007-2012: Expansion</h2>
  <p>During this period, the organization significantly expanded its scope of activities. Work began on environmental monitoring, community development and protection of vulnerable groups.</p>

  <h2>2013-2018: Consolidation</h2>
  <p>The organization strengthened its reputation as one of the leading human rights associations in Kyrgyzstan. Large-scale projects on election monitoring, anti-corruption activities and media development were implemented.</p>

  <h2>2019-Present</h2>
  <p>Active work continues in all areas of activity. The organization adapts to new challenges, introduces modern working methods and expands its partner network.</p>
</PageLayout>
